headline: The Mosaic Company (MOS) Had a Difficult 2024
summary: White Brook Capital Partners, an investment management firm, released its fourth-quarter 2024 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. White Brook Capital’s middle capitalization focused fund had a forgettable year in 2024. With the announcement of fourth-quarter earnings and positive 2025 outlook by the fund’s portfolio companies, fortunes have turned around […]
